Class PSLModelLoader

  • java.lang.Object
      • edu.umd.cs.psl.parser.PSLBaseVisitor<Formula>
        • edu.umd.cs.psl.parser.PSLModelLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PSLVisitor<Formula>

    public class PSLModelLoader
extends PSLBaseVisitor<Formula>
    This class operates both as a utility class to load PSL models as well as the visitor implementation for the ANTLR PSL model parser. TODO: Implement set predicates and external functions (perhaps a standard library of built-in external functions)
